# Space Facts Generator ðŸŒŽ ðŸš€

A simple, elegant web application that displays random interesting facts about space. Built with vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this project features a modern, space-themed design with a responsive interface.

## Features

- Display random space facts with a single click
- 20 curated interesting facts about space
- Responsive design that works on all devices
- Modern glassmorphism UI elements
- Smooth animations and transitions

## Live Demo

To use the application, simply open the `index.html` file in a web browser.

